# Post-Edit Verification

After editing any `.svelte` or `.ts` file in `src/`:

1. Run `npm run check` (svelte-kit sync + svelte-check)
2. Run `npm run lint` (prettier + eslint)
3. Run `npm run knip`
4. **When logic or behavior changed** (e.g. `src/lib/**`, algorithms, state flow, or anything that could regress): also run `npm run test`
5. Fix any reported issues — do not consider the task complete until all invoked checks pass

For Svelte components: also run `svelte-autofixer` and iterate until no issues remain (see svelte-code-quality rule).
